title: Episode 236: Nene...leaks (Feat. Nene Leakes)
itunes:title: Episode 236: Nene...leaks (Feat. Nene Leakes)
description:
RHOA's Nene Leakes joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and opens up about the time she caught her ex cheating at work, the struggles of being married for a long time, her bad experiences with porn, and much more. Nene even shoots her shot at Angela, saying she's the only one she'll have a threesome with. Enjoy!
